<h1>Aspect</h1>

<p>Aspect, unlike tense, is not always marked.  There are three types of aspect, punctual, imperfective and perfective.  Aspect is only used with active verbs since it is used to describe actions in a flow of time.</p>

<h3>Punctual Aspect</h3>
